# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the values.
# `.env.local` is git-ignored so your real key never leaves your machine.

# Google Maps API key.
#
# Required for:
#   - Address autocomplete in the invoice listing editor and event modal.
#   - Auto-calculated driving distance + travel fees (Distance Matrix).
#
# If this is unset, the app still works — autocomplete inputs fall back to
# plain text fields, and travel fees are entered manually in the listing
# editor. Useful for development without a billing-enabled GCP project.
#
# To create a key:
#   1. Visit https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#   2. Create (or pick) a project and click "Create credentials" → "API key"
#   3. Restrict the key by:
#      - HTTP referrers: your production domain + http://localhost:*/*
#      - APIs: "Places API", "Distance Matrix API", "Maps JavaScript API"
#   4. Paste the key below.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
